"Articles"
Three text boxes
- Title - Mandatory
- Snippet - Mandatory
- Link - Mandatory
Submit -- this is a form, submit button is more of a save button

ArticleList contains this form^^^, list of articles comes from the ArticleContainer

In each listing on main page:
Title
"See More" button
"delete button"

Once "See more" is clicked, modal renders with Title, Snippet, and link to full article.

ArticleItem
renders the modal, with the item details if button is clicked
the only stateful thing in ArticleItem is the the modal hook

step 1: build the form
step 2: make sure the right thing renders
step 3: create the modal component
step 4: use the modal inside the article item

